<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"/>
  <title>Race Riot</title>

</head>
<body>

<!-- HTML FOR WEBPAGE  -->

  <nav class="blue" role="navigation">
    <div class="nav-wrapper container">
      <a id="logo-container" href="cb_360.png" height="55" width="55" class="brand-logo">Logo</a>
      <ul class="right hide-on-med-and-down">
        <li><a href="#map">Visualization</a></li>
      </ul>

      <ul id="nav-mobile" class="side-nav">
        <li><a href="#">Navbar Link</a></li>
      </ul>
      <a href="#" data-activates="nav-mobile" class="button-collapse"><i class="mdi-navigation-menu"></i></a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div id="index-banner" class="parallax-container">
    <div class="section no-pad-bot">
      <div class="container">
        <br><br>
        <div class="row center">
          <a href="#map"><button class="btn-large waves-effect waves-light blue">Show Me The Map</button></a>
        </div>
        <br><br>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="parallax">
      <video autoplay loop poster="riot-police-sarajevo.jpg" id="bgvid">
      <source src="/assets/movie.mp4" type="video/mp4">
      </video>
    </div>
    </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="section">

      <!--   Icon Section   -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="mdi-image-flash-on"></i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Data That Matters</h5>

            <p class="light">We believe context is critical, especially within the confines of the social and political circumstances of our time. Here we try to capture some of that context through historical data and presenting that information in a potentially meaningful way.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="mdi-social-group"></i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Raise Awareness</h5>

            <p class="light">Amid various lenses through which the media represents information, specifically their coverage of events involving racial tension, we want to present data and let it speak for itself.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="mdi-action-settings"></i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">There Is Work To Be Done</h5>

            <p class="light">We have begun the process of compiling this information, but a visualization is only as good and as accurate as its data. In that vein, we welcome your participation in this process by signing up and contributing data on a recent or past event. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="map-section">
    <div class="action-section">

			<form>
				<input type="text" placeholder="e.g. 1950" class="year_data">
        <button class="btn waves-effect waves-light blue find_year" type="submit" name="action">Submit
          <i class="mdi-content-send right"></i>
        </button>
        <br>

			</form>
      <a class="waves-effect waves-light blue btn generate-data">Show it all</a>

      <a name="map"></a>
    	<form class='display-form'>
				<input type="text" name="before_year" class="before_year" placeholder="Before Year" value='2015'>
        <input type="text" name="after_year" class="after_year" placeholder="After Year" value='1960'>

        <a class="waves-effect waves-light blue btn submit_display_year submit_display">Display</a>
      </form>

			<div class="map-container">
			</div>

			<div class="data-container1">
			</div>
			<div class="data-container2">
			</div>


    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="footer-copyright light-blue darken-4 charlie">
    Made by Charlie Brown
  </footer>

  </body>
</html>
